headline: This 9%-Plus Yielder Just Raised Its Dividend
summary: Friday, LyondellBasell raised its quarterly dividend to $1.37 a share from $1.34. It’s a 2% increase, but still, it qualifies as a surprise because the stock yielded more than 9% ahead of the hike.

headline: LyondellBasell Hikes Quarterly Dividend for 15 Consecutive Years
summary: LYB raises quarterly dividend to $1.37, marking 15 straight years of growth and reinforcing its shareholder value strategy.
